{"tid":1254961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6月26日（三）20:00-21:00 愛丁堡廣場 香港人！G20峰會前再集結！","createTime":"2019-06-24T10:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T10:31:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"765e3c8e03f2d9db31bb4e12c00fdcadf67a26ed","tid":1254961,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"6月26日（三）20:00-21:00 愛丁堡廣場 香港人！G20峰會前再集結！<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n香港人！G20峰會前再集結！<br />\n<br />\n林鄭仍未回應民間五大訴求，道歉欠缺誠意，另一方面逃犯條例修訂在建制派之間嘗試死灰復燃，我們希望在國際大事：G20峰會之前，再度與香港人集結，在國際壓力上再給予林鄭月娥重重一擊！香港人，頂住！<br />\n<br />\nG20 Free Hong Kong集會<br />\n日期：6月26日（三）<br />\n地點：愛丁堡廣場<br />\n時間：20:00-21:00<br />\n<br />\nHongkongers! Let&rsquo;s rally before G20!<br />\n<br />\nCarrie Lam has yet to respond to the five demands from civil society. Her apology was insincere. At the same time, a pro-establishment legislator is trying to revive the suspended extradition bill! The G20 Summit will take place on 28 June. Before this important event on the international stage, we should rally again to deal another blow to Carrie Lam! Hongkongers, stand firm!<br />\n<br />\nG20 Free Hong Kong Assembly<br />\nDate: June 26 (Wed)<br />\nVenue: Edinburgh Place, Central<br />\nTime: 20:00-21:00<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2314873311893380/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.517931904920872%2F2314873311893380%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVLTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=05524237\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2314873311893380/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"bd5566ec0b67d14df9e73b6b2e37d042714abad1","tid":1254961,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/65006784_2314873321893379_7730433012399079424_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmG-zptNBtdym3rP7rB7b9dmsN5fZ6vj-Y4zbvC09BVPbKheKVbQCOxj7yRW3cnW0M&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=ba46f2dbe48a9e492a148dd5e8503cfa&amp;oe=5DBD4C23\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F65006784_2314873321893379_7730433012399079424_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmG-zptNBtdym3rP7rB7b9dmsN5fZ6vj-Y4zbvC09BVPbKheKVbQCOxj7yRW3cnW0M%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Dba46f2dbe48a9e492a148dd5e8503cfa%26oe%3D5DBD4C23&h=38671cab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b94bca01ef812bdbb11c7948e586761793181ae1","tid":1254961,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc3cb742610b4011839c6c7234aa64cf80e3c467","tid":1254961,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}